### 获取用户的提现单列表

GET http://{{host}}/api/rest/views/finance/withdraws/1?_format=json&created[min]=2018-01-01&created[max]=2018-05-12
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 创建用户的转账方式

POST http://{{host}}/entity/finance_transfer_method?_format=json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "type": "alipay",
  "transfer_gateway": "alipay",
  "name": "sdfsdf",
  "user_id": "1",
  "alipay_name": "王哈哈",
  "alipay_account": "1267867@qq.com"
}

### 修改一个转账方式

PATCH http://{{host}}/admin/finance/finance_transfer_method/2?_format=json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "type": "alipay",
  "name": "sdfsdf",
  "alipay_name": "王哈哈",
  "alipay_account": "155555@qq.com"
}

